<a name="PeIdle(float, int, int)"><img src="images/red-ball.gif" width=12 height=12 alt=" o "></a>
<a name="PeIdle"><b>PeIdle</b></a>
<pre>
 public abstract void PeIdle(float time,
                             int PeId,
                             int reason)
</pre>
<dl>
  <dd> Invoked when a PE has become idle for some reason
<p>
  <dd><dl>
    <dt> <b>Parameters:</b>
    <dd> time - Time when the PE became idle
    <dd> PeId - The id of the PE that became idle
    <dd> reason - Why the PE became idle. Not implemented.
  </dl></dd>
</dl>
