<a name="EndOfTimeSlice"><b>EndOfTimeSlice</b></a>
<pre>
 public abstract void EndOfTimeSlice(float time,
                                     int PeId)
</pre>
<dl>
  <dd> Invoked when a timeslice has expired on a PE.
<p>
  <dd><dl>
    <dt> <b>Parameters:</b>
    <dd> time - Time when the timeslice expired
    <dd> PeId - The id of the PE at which the timeslice has expired
  </dl></dd>
</dl>
